                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text VI is ascribed to ʾabba Yoḥannǝs, the Patriarch of Constantinople whereas in Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESkae015">KAE-015</ref>a similar text (Text V) is ascribed to ʾabba Sawiros. In Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESkae001">KAE-001</ref>the homily is anonymous.</note>
                     <note>- The incipit of Text VII is referred as ድርሳን ዘገብርኤል but the actual content is Miracles of Gabriel.</note>
                  </msItem>
